People ex rel. Graham, Supervisor, v. Board of Supervisors. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. October 19, 1888.) Certiorari on the relation of Alexander Graham, to review the proceedings of the board of supervisors of Wayne county in equalizing assessments. This case was heard with and follows People v. Board of Supervisors, 2 H. Y. Supp. 555.

Argued before Haight, Bradley, and Dwight, JJ.

J. W. Dunwell, for relator. C. H. Roys, for respondent.

Ho opinion. Certiorari quashed without costs to either party. All concur.
